column5: We were out on Simcoe looking for some Pike on Saturday. Pretty slow except for one little hot spot that produced non stop action for about an hour. I didn't get a weight or length, as the pike flopped out of the boat when I tried to put it on the lip grip. Oh well, at least I got a nice photo.  Cheers!
nice pike thanks for the report
nice job, you deffinately picked a nice day for it. How deep were you guys fishing?
That's a pretty respectable fish there, Thanks for the pic.
NIce pike for sure. Thanks for posting!
